name: Transaction Report
query:
select name, date_of_transaction, exporter_name as Exporter, forwarder_name as Forwarder, 
consignee_name as Consignee, quantity as Quantity, weight as Weight, cargo_description as 'Cargo Description', 
consignee_country as Country from tabTransaction 
where date_of_transaction between %(date_from)s AND %(date_to)s
